spans.text: Who follow but where judgement points the way , And whom too busy sense never led astray
a reign ? — the walk is over , The dinner waits , and friends some half a score
Excuse — " It's hot , and walking makes one faint
Hopes for what never was , nor ever will be : The nearest ease , since we must suffer still , Are they , who dare be patient under ill
no rot , his corn no blight
